Mark Mobius Sees ‘Incredible’ Investment Potential in Africa

-- B y   K a n a   N i s h i z a w a
-- 
2011-05-30T03:52:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/mark-mobius-sees-an-incredible-investment-potential-in-african-continent.html
Mark Mobius , executive chairman of
Templeton Asset Management’s emerging markets group, said  Africa 
has an “incredible” investment potential and that he has a big
investment in Nigerian banks.  Mobius made the comments in  Tokyo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
